comment.brief: Only the most recent ancestor navigation considered. A page can be active in the local navigation, even if that navigation resides in a page which is not active itself.

comment.brief: The full path is considered  -- from here through all navigation instances to the root. A page is only active if all it's ancestor pages are active.
